===Summary===
*[[Seasonal/Christmas 2016|Christmas]] Seasonal Content will end on 26th December at 00:00 Hours (12 AM) JST.
* Anyone can receives an one time [[Present Box]] from the developer if they log in before December 25th 24:00.
* AA guns and anti-torpedo bulges can now be equipped on Reinforcement Expansion slots.
* New Anti-Torpedo bulge equipment
* Akashi's Improvement Arsenal can now be accessed by clicking on the bottom-left crane in the composition page with Akashi as the flagship.
* Akashi's Improvement Arsenal now shows remaining equipment available to be consumed when upgrading.
* New equipment available for improvement in Akashi's Improvement Arsenal.
