===[[Reinforcement Expansion]] Buff===
The following equipment types can now be equipped on the expansion slot:
*{{GreenGunMG}}[[List of Anti-Air Guns by stats|Anti-Air guns]]
*{{ArmorEquipment}}Anti-Torpedo bulges
<br />
{{GreenGunMG}}Anti-Air guns equipped in expansion slots can help ships like {{ShipLink|Kinu/Kai Ni}} and {{ShipLink|Maya/Kai Ni}} trigger [http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/Aerial_Combat#Anti-Air_Cut-In AACI], meaning that it frees up a main slot for other uses. For example, it is now possible to equip a {{Seaplane}}Seaplane on {{ShipLink|Maya/Kai Ni}} for [[Artillery Spotting]] while allowing her to [http://kancolle.wikia.com/wiki/Aerial_Combat#Anti-Air_Cut-In AACI] at the same time.
<br />

