===[[Akashi's Improvement Arsenal]]===
*[[Akashi's Improvement Arsenal]] can now be accessed by clicking on the bottom-left crane in the composition page with Akashi as the flagship.
*[[Akashi's Improvement Arsenal]] now displays the amount of the required equipment you have left before the improvement, if the equipment improvement requires another equipment.
*{{ArmorEquipment}}[[Anti-torpedo Bulge (Large)]] and {{ArmorEquipment}}[[New Kanhon Design Anti-torpedo Bulge (Large)]] can now be improved in [[Akashi's Improvement Arsenal]].
* {{ArmorEquipment}}[[Anti-torpedo Bulge (Large)]] can now be further improved into {{ArmorEquipment}} [[New Kanhon Design Anti-torpedo Bulge (Large)]]
